# Standardize on LF line endings on every platform.
# Prevents Windows core.autocrlf from CRLF-converting files on checkout, which
# breaks preflight Check 4 (*.sh must be LF) and can corrupt checksum'd blobs
# (crlfcheckout, C.1.3.2 pattern — applied repo-wide C.1.4.x).
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh   text eol=lf
*.js   text eol=lf
*.mjs  text eol=lf
*.cjs  text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md   text eol=lf
*.yml  text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.txt  text eol=lf
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.zip binary
*.app binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
